    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[夜钓]]></title>
        <id>https://lztmdrclht.github.io/post/ye-diao/</id>
        <link href="https://lztmdrclht.github.io/post/ye-diao/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-09-30T13:05:12.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>你将渔线放啊放，沉入大海，钓鲸鱼</p>
<p>我将风筝放啊放，升入夜空</p>
<p>钓星星</p>
]]></content>
